'''Sealord of Braavos''' is the title held by the ruler of [[Braavos]], one of the [[Free Cities]] in the continent of [[Essos]].

For nine years [[Syrio Forel]] was [[First Sword of Braavos|First Sword]] to the Sealord of Braavos.
